Hello, thank you for contacting NoteWorthy, where we turn music into memories. My name is Gabriel Phillips. May I have your name, please?

Hi Gabriel, my name is Lauren Adams. I'm calling because I'm really frustrated about my recent bill.

I am sorry to hear that, Lauren. I am here to help. Could you please provide me with your account number so I can look into this for you?

Sure, my account number is one two three four five.

Thank you for that information. Can you also confirm the email address associated with your account?

It's lauren.adams@email.com.

Thank you, Lauren. I have pulled up your account. I see the issue here, and I apologize for the confusion. It seems there was an error in the billing system.

It's been really frustrating dealing with this.

I completely understand your frustration. Let's get this resolved today. I will correct this and ensure a revised bill is sent to you.

Thank you for your patience, Lauren. Is there anything else I can assist you with?

No, that was it. Thank you for your help, Gabriel.

You're welcome. Thank you for your time, Lauren. Have a great day!
